title: STEREO-B/WAVES/HFR Data - Milan Maksimovic (milan.maksimovic@obspm.fr) and Stuart D. Bale (bale@berkeley.edu) (LESIA, Observatoire de Paris-PSL, CNRS and UC Berkeley Space Sciences Laboratory)

info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'Epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/stereo/behind/l3/waves/hfr/2006/stb_l3_wav_hfr_20061030_v01.cdf. The most common cadence occurred for 3.6788% of the 126 timesteps. Cadence = 24179993570 [ns] = PT24.179994S.
info.contact: Milan Maksimovic (milan.maksimovic@obspm.fr) and Stuart D. Bale (bale@berkeley.edu) @ LESIA, Observatoire de Paris-PSL, CNRS and UC Berkeley Space Sciences Laboratory

parameters.name: Time
parameters.x_description: Epoch encoded as Terrestrial Time on rotating Earth geoid, ns since J2000

parameters.name: PSD_FLUX
parameters.description: Power spectral density after 1% background subtraction and antenna calibration

parameters.name: PSD_SFU
parameters.description: Power spectral density after 1% background subtraction and antenna calibration in solar radio flux unit normalized to 1 au

parameters.name: SOURCE_SIZE
parameters.description: The angular half aperture of the source as seen by a spacecraft (uniform profile) [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_COLATITUDE_RTN
parameters.description: Wave vector colatitude in the Radial-Tangential-Normal (RTN) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_AZIMUTH_RTN
parameters.description: Wave vector azimuth in the Radial-Tangential-Normal (RTN) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_COLATITUDE_HCI
parameters.description: Wave vector colatitude in the Heliocentric Inertial (HCI) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_AZIMUTH_HCI
parameters.description: Wave vector azimuth in the Heliocentric Inertial (HCI) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_COLATITUDE_HEE
parameters.description: Wave vector colatitude in the Heliocentric Earth Ecliptic (HEE) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_AZIMUTH_HEE
parameters.description: Wave vector azimuth in the Heliocentric Earth Ecliptic (HEE) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_COLATITUDE_HEEQ
parameters.description: Wave vector colatitude in the Heliocentric Earth Equatorial (HEEQ) system [Data available after 04-May-2007]

parameters.name: WAVE_AZIMUTH_HEEQ
